                    <span>This is a great, tragic play.  It's not too hard to read, and it's pretty short (!), so you could read it in a day probably.  This play will have you questioning what you would do in both Antigone's and Creon's situations, so you know it's pretty good.  And the important question: who's the tragic hero?!?  I'm still deciding</span>
                  
